lar tagging/ FISH-analysis and confocal laser scanning microscopy to study details of root colonization by the studied bacteria; whole genome analysis of Acidovorax radicis N35 and Rhizobium radiobacter F4 using 454-pyrosequencing (Titanium technology, Roche Co.). Contact person : Prof. Dr. Yahai Lu (Tel.: 62733617; email: yhlu@cau.edu.cn ) or Dr. Ke Ma (Tel.:62731358; email: markinlord@gmail.com ) 中国农业大学资源与环境学院 
